data.description: Perfect Location in Dublin Schools!  This 4 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath, 2-Story is Open and Spacious! Newer Appliances in Kitchen w/Lots of Cabinets & Counter Space. Eat-In Area w/Bay Window! Huge Vaulted Great Room w/Ceiling Fan/Light, Raised Hearth Fireplace & Lots of Windows!  Formal Living & Dining Rooms! 1st Floor Laundry/Mud Room! Vaulted Master Suite w/Dual Vanities, Separate Shower & Soaking Tub & Walk-In Closet! New Ceiling Fans! Finished LL!  New HVAC in 2017!  Fire Pit & Deck. Close To Everything - Schools, Shopping, Bike Paths & More!  Sold As-Is.
